==Manx==
===Etymology===
From {{inh|gv|sga|íarn}}, from {{inh|gv|cel-pro|*īsarnom}} (compare {{cog|cy|haearn}}, {{cog|br|houarn}}), probably from {{inh|gv|ine-pro|*h₁ēsh₂r̥no-||bloody, red}}, from {{m|ine-pro|*h₁ésh₂r̥||(flowing) blood}}.
===Noun===
